					&lt;p&gt;Don't think it's a marketing trick. Imagine all the costs to get the lemon slices out of the bottles.&lt;/p&gt;

					&lt;p&gt;Lemon in general goes very good with beer. In Germany (not only there) a mixture of beer and lemonade is very common and famous (called Radler or Alsterwasser).&lt;/p&gt;

